Text: What is this? Bootleg? Fan compilation?

I can't find ANY info about this album so it seems to just be a fancompilation. I guess all the tracks can easily be found elsewhere. 'I Got Erection' and 'Selfdestructo Bust' are live-versions.
Too bad they fucked up the release by cutting 'Selfdestructo Bust' to short. It ends in the middle of a goddamn word!
This thing will get DELETED from my HD.
